142
00:06:26.210 --> 00:06:27.920
I run with Fuli every day.

143
00:06:28.920 --> 00:06:30.540
I'll get to Udugu first!

144
00:06:30.540 --> 00:06:32.170
Oh, no, you won't!

145
00:06:33.499 --> 00:06:34.669
(GRUNTING)

146
00:06:34.669 --> 00:06:36.789
