anything, couldn't you?

147
00:06:38.330 --> 00:06:39.420
BOTH: Yes!

148
00:06:40.580 --> 00:06:41.710
(SIGHS)

149
00:06:41.710 --> 00:06:43.380
At least you agree on that.

150
00:06:43.380 --> 00:06:46.040
Come on.
We have a long way to go.

151
00:06:48.209 --> 00:06:49.919
(EAGLE SCREECHING)

152
00:06:53.250 --> 00:06:54.710
ONO: Uh, Your Majesty?

153
00:06:55.330 --> 00:06:56.960
Yes, Ono?

154
00:06:56.960 --> 00:06:59.920
Well, it's not
a big deal...

155
00:06:59.920 --> 00:07:01.879
But, uh...
Ono's trying to say that

156
00:07:01.880 --> 00:07:04.330
on morning patrol,
Kion usually goes this way.

157
00:07:05.500 --> 00:07:06.880
Is that so?

158
00:07:06.880 --> 00:07:09.580
And is Kion here?

159
00:07:11.499 --> 00:07:13.379
No, sir.
You heard the King.

160
00:07:13.380 --> 00:07:15.330
We'll go this way
for a change.

161
00:07:15.330 --> 00:07:16.830
It'll be fun.

162
00:07:16.830 --> 00:07:18.620
Yes. "Fun."

163
00:07:21.080 --> 00:07:24.330
Mom, how much longer
will it take to get to Udugu?

164
00:07:24.330 --> 00:07:26.499
That's a tough question.

165
00:07:26.500 --> 00:07:29.040
Udugu isn't easy to find.

166
00:07:29.040 --> 00:07:31.210
Don't worry, I'll find it.

167
00:07:31.210 --> 00:07:32.960
I'm a better tracker
than you.

168
00:07:32.960 --> 00:07:34.580
We'll see about that!

169
00:07:34.580 --> 00:07:36.999
(BOTH LAUGHING)

170
00:07:36.999 --> 00:07:39.999
You really think you can
find Udugu before me?

171
00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:41.420
Just watch me.

172
00:07:43.710 --> 00:07:45.670
Kion, Kiara, be careful!

173
00:07:45.670 --> 00:07:46.669
(BOTH GASP)

174
00:07:49.380 --> 00:07:50.880
I got you.

175
00:07:55.120 --> 00:07:56.500
Thanks, Mom.
Thanks.

176
00:07:56.500 --> 00:07:59.580
That is definitely not
the way to find Udugu.

177
00:08:01.880 --> 00:08:03.420
(RUMBLING IN DISTANCE)

178
