(GASPS)

179
00:08:10.039 --> 00:08:11.169
ONO: <i>Hapana!</i>

180
00:08:11.169 --> 00:08:12.539
Everyone, look! A...

181
00:08:12.539 --> 00:08:14.249
A mud slide!
Straight ahead!

182
00:08:14.250 --> 00:08:16.000
Uh, yes, sire.

183
00:08:16.000 --> 00:08:17.330
ONO: And the mud's headed
right for...

184
00:08:17.330 --> 00:08:18.920
The ostrich herd's nest!

185
00:08:18.961 --> 00:08:21.961
If we don't move fast,
the mud will sweep the eggs
off the cliff!

186
00:08:21.961 --> 00:08:23.039
Affirmative.

187
00:08:23.039 --> 00:08:24.619
I was just about to say that.

188
00:08:24.619 --> 00:08:26.499
We'll have to act fast.

189
00:08:26.541 --> 00:08:30.621
I'll move that log,
so it diverts the mud
away from the nest!

190
00:08:30.621 --> 00:08:31.960
What should we do?

191
00:08:31.960 --> 00:08:34.500
Just stick together
and follow me.

192
00:08:35.579 --> 00:08:38.379
Just stick together
and follow him?

193
00:08:38.380 --> 00:08:39.540
That's what he said.

194
00:08:39.540 --> 00:08:41.040
And he is the King.

195
00:08:41.040 --> 00:08:42.670
Our eggs!
Our eggs!

196
00:08:44.540 --> 00:08:45.620
This way, Lion Guard!

197
00:08:45.620 --> 00:08:47.289
Jump from rock to rock!

198
00:08:47.289 --> 00:08:49.709
Uh, jump from
rock to rock?

199
00:08:49.710 --> 00:08:51.830
Usually, Kion just has me
run through the mud.

200
00:08:51.830 --> 00:08:54.170
Yeah, but Kion's not
in charge right now.

201
00:08:54.170 --> 00:08:55.500
Simba is.

202
00:08:55.500 --> 00:08:57.170
Lion Guard,
come on!

203
00:08:57.211 --> 00:09:00.501
